MPGA for C++
=================

MPGA - Make Perl great again - Flow-driven development library for C++


USAGE

#include "mpga.hpp"
#include <iostream>
#include <string>

auto step1 = [](int a, int b) {
    return a + b;
};

auto step2 = [](int result, std::string prefix) {
    std::cout << "  " << prefix << ": " << result << "\n";
};

flow(10, 20, step1, std::string("Result is"), step2);


COMPILATION

clang++ -std=c++23 7.cpp


